examples.en: He described the scene in meticulous detail.
The attack was meticulously planned and executed.
The book describes his journey in meticulous detail.
He cleaned the tools with meticulous care.
He has always been so meticulous about his appearance.
He was meticulous in his use of words.
Their planning and preparation were meticulous.
He is meticulous about keeping accurate records.
Note the meticulous precision of his measurements.
He is almost worryingly meticulous in his business formalities.
She was very much the craftswoman, all her work meticulous, slow, perfect.
